            <p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <p>
                    <md>
                      <mrow>\revenue_x (x,y)\amp = \frac{-24x-5y+1000}{600} </mrow>
                      <mrow>\revenue_y (x,y)\amp = \frac{-3x-16y+10800}{360} </mrow>
                    </md>
                  </p>
                </li>

                <li>
                  <p>
                    Using WolframALpha, the critical point is at <m>(62000/123, 23800/41)  \approx (504, 580.5)</m>.
                  </p>

